          "range": "463-502",
          "rangeStart": 463,
          "rangeEnd": 502,
          "markText": "约在10年以前，我还不曾想起要为先曾祖父宗棠公写点什么，更不用说一本完整的传。",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1721185384,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-07-17 11:03:04",
          "chapterUid": 3,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300015575&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=463&rangeEnd=502",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/09932220813ab6c95g015bba?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=463&rangeEnd=502"
        }
      ]
