  ],
  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300015575_15_3433-3481",
      "chapterUid": 15,
      "range": "3433-3481",
      "markText": "其实，诸葛亮只辅助了一个偏安王朝，而且是在内战中以失败告终，左宗棠的功业和军事才能是超过诸葛的。",
      "totalCount": 304,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300015575&chapterUid=15&rangeStart=3433&rangeEnd=3481",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/09932220813ab6c95g015bba?chapterUid=15&rangeStart=3433&rangeEnd=3481"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300015575_18_2706-2743",
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "range": "2706-2743",
      "markText": "他这两条建议如能被清廷采纳，也许英法联军打不到北京，圆明园也不会被烧毁了。",
      "totalCount": 176,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300015575&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=2706&rangeEnd=2743",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/09932220813ab6c95g015bba?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=2706&rangeEnd=2743"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300015575_23_3694-3749",
      "chapterUid": 23,
      "range": "3694-3749",
      "markText": "在山本清，泉自源头冷起； 入世皆幻，峰从天外飞来。",
      "totalCount": 144,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300015575&chapterUid=23&rangeStart=3694&rangeEnd=3749",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/09932220813ab6c95g015bba?chapterUid=23&rangeStart=3694&rangeEnd=3749"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300015575_8_8004-8089",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "8004-8089",
      "markText": "左宗棠的科举道路是坎坷的，也可说命运不济。但是如果他果真中了进士，点上翰林，他的后半生可能又是另一番面目了。他自幼就不重视科举，这注定了所追求的是有价值的另一条生活道路。",
      "totalCount": 128,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300015575&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=8004&rangeEnd=8089",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/09932220813ab6c95g015bba?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=8004&rangeEnd=8089"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300015575_9_1421-1446",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "1421-1446",
      "markText": "见我，他来看我好了。我又无求于他，为何要去见他？”",
      "totalCount": 120,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300015575&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=1421&rangeEnd=1446",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/09932220813ab6c95g015bba?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=1421&rangeEnd=1446"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300015575_8_4392-4549",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "4392-4549",
      "markText": "西域环兵不计年，当时立国重开边。 橐驼万里输官稻，沙碛千秋此石田。 置省尚烦它日策，兴屯宁费度支钱？ 将军莫更纾愁眼，生计中原亦可怜。",
      "totalCount": 119,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300015575&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=4392&rangeEnd=4549",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/09932220813ab6c95g015bba?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=4392&rangeEnd=4549"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300015575_64_7683-7730",
      "chapterUid": 64,
      "range": "7683-7730",
      "markText": "绝口不言和议事； 千秋独有左文襄！",
      "totalCount": 119,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300015575&chapterUid=64&rangeStart=7683&rangeEnd=7730",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/09932220813ab6c95g015bba?chapterUid=64&rangeStart=7683&rangeEnd=7730"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300015575_7_2606-2657",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "2606-2657",
      "markText": "身无半亩，心忧天下； 读破万卷，神交古人。",
      "totalCount": 112,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300015575&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2606&rangeEnd=2657",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/09932220813ab6c95g015bba?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2606&rangeEnd=2657"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300015575_40_4936-4990",
      "chapterUid": 40,
      "range": "4936-4990",
      "markText": "他首先认定新疆是一块无用的地方，中国拥有新疆这块160万平方公里肥沃富饶的土地，是得不偿失，这是何等的荒谬！",
      "totalCount": 112,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300015575&chapterUid=40&rangeStart=4936&rangeEnd=4990",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/09932220813ab6c95g015bba?chapterUid=40&rangeStart=4936&rangeEnd=4990"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300015575_5_4547-4576",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "4547-4576",
      "markText": "40余年后他在杭州，一次游天竺、灵隐，恍惚是当日梦中所见。",
      "totalCount": 108,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300015575&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=4547&rangeEnd=4576",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/09932220813ab6c95g015bba?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=4547&rangeEnd=4576"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300015575_6_1661-1730",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "1661-1730",
      "markText": "熙龄教学生的方针与一般人不同，他不重视八股文，和哥哥长龄一样，注重“经世致用”的实学。他用汉宋以来实学家的著作教学生，这正符合宗棠的志趣。",
